            <!-- Project 1 -->
            <article class="project">
                <h2>Project 1: Wildlife Reserve</h2>
                <p>
                    The Wildlife Reserve project is dedicated to protecting endangered species and preserving their natural habitats. This initiative focuses on creating safe, sustainable environments where wildlife can thrive without the threat of human encroachment, poaching, or environmental degradation.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Establishing protected zones with monitored boundaries.</li>
                    <li>Rehabilitating and reforesting degraded landscapes to restore ecosystems.</li>
                    <li>Collaborating with local communities to promote coexistence and reduce conflicts with wildlife.</li>
                    <li>Conducting educational programs to raise awareness about biodiversity conservation.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>This project serves as a beacon of hope for preserving Earth's precious flora and fauna for future generations.</p>
                
                <!-- Conservation Image for Project 1 -->
                <div class="conservation-image">
