                </div>
            </article>
            
            <!-- Project 2 -->
            <article class="project">
                <h2>Project 2: Sustainable Living</h2>
                <p>
                    The Sustainable Living project promotes eco-friendly practices and technologies to reduce environmental impact and foster a greener future. It focuses on empowering individuals and communities to adopt sustainable habits and resources.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Encouraging the use of renewable energy sources like solar and wind power.</li>
                    <li>Organizing workshops on waste management, recycling, and composting.</li>
                    <li>Supporting sustainable agriculture practices, such as organic farming and water conservation techniques.</li>
                    <li>Promoting green building designs and energy-efficient technologies in homes and workplaces.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The project emphasizes the importance of small, collective actions in creating a significant positive impact on the planet, ensuring a sustainable lifestyle for generations to come.</p>
                
